EventItemActionText: A motion was made that this Resolution be Approved, by Council approved by Voice Vote.
EventItemTitle: Resolution calling upon the Governor and the New York State Legislature to amend that section of the New York State General Business Law known as the Pistol and Revolver Ballistic Identification Databank Law, to require that assault weapons, rifles and other long-barreled weapons be included in New York State’s ballistics fingerprint database.
EventItemMatterName: Amend the Pistol and Revolver Ballistic Identification Databank Law.

EventItemActionText: This Resolution was Approved, by Council
EventItemTitle: Resolution calling upon the New York State Legislature to amend various sections of the Penal Law to better combat illegal gun trafficking.
EventItemMatterName: Amend Penal Law to better combat illegal gun trafficking.

EventItemActionText: This Resolution was Approved, by Council
EventItemTitle: Resolution calling upon the United States Congress to approve legislation that establishes a national ballistics fingerprint database.
EventItemMatterName: "Ballistics, Law Assistance, and Safety Technology Act" ("BLAST Act")

EventItemActionText: A motion was made that this Resolution be Approved, by Council approved by Voice Vote.
EventItemTitle: Resolution calling on the State Legislature to amend the Penal Law to include the denial of a weapons permit for any applicant convicted of violating New York City’s assault weapons ban.
EventItemMatterName: Amend the Penal Law to include the denial of a weapons permit for any applicant convicted of violating NYC’s assault weapons ban.
